videos.description: Karl-Anthony Towns grabs his own miss and scores the first points of the game against the Nuggets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Towns keeps it alive for first bucket) 2018/04/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Towns keeps it alive for first bucket

videos.description: The Nuggets grab the offensive board then Will Barton explodes to the inside, flipping the ball up to score the crazy shot for a chance at a 3-point play.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Barton scores wild and-1 basket) 2018/04/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Barton scores wild and-1 basket

videos.description: Taj Gibson crosses over Nikola Jokic then scores a layup and the Minnesota crowd stands up in excitement.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gibson's layup fires up crowd) 2018/04/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gibson's layup fires up crowd

videos.description: Jamal Crawford bounces it to Jimmy Butler who rises up and jams it in the hoop to give the Timberwolves their largest lead of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Minnesota fans light up after Butler's dunk) 2018/04/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Minnesota fans light up after Butler's dunk

videos.description: With less than three minutes to go in regulation, Jamal Murray drills a 3-pointer over Taj Gibson to tie the score 99-99.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Murray nails 3 to tie score) 2018/04/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Murray nails 3 to tie score

videos.description: Andrew Wiggins finds Jeff Teague, who swishes a floater to give the Timberwolves a 107-106 lead in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Wiggins, Teague connect for clutch shot) 2018/4/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wiggins, Teague connect for clutch shot

videos.description: In the final 25 seconds of overtime, Will Barton misses a crucial basket and Karl-Anthony Towns grabs it to secure the Timberwolves' first playoff berth since 2004.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Nuggets miss critical shot in OT) 2018/04/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nuggets miss critical shot in OT
